  "texts": [
    "Below, we describe the application of DNN, CNN, and CNN-LSTM deep learning architectures using the preprocessed data.",
    "First, Total 60-dimensional MFCC feature vectors were used as input data for the DNN architecture by combining the 20-dimensional MFCC extracted from three sections of each signal.",
    "The DNN architecture consists of an input layer, an output layer, and three hidden layers.",
    "The number of nodes for the three hidden layers was set to 36, 22 and 13 respectively, which were activated by the ReLU function.",
    "The final output layer activated by Softmax function distinguishes the six classes for each gas species."
  ],
